# dev-factory.env — operator config for run.sh (copy this to `dev-factory.env` and edit).
#
# This is YOUR config, not the plugin's: keep the filled-in copy in your project / operator space, never
# commit it into the plugin. run.sh sources it (or $DEV_FACTORY_ENV, or <instance>/run.env) and launches.
# Only DEV_FACTORY_DIR is required; everything else has a sensible default.

# ── required ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your instance — the .agents/dev-factory dir under your project (created by /factory-init or lattice.py init).
DEV_FACTORY_DIR=/path/to/your-project/.agents/dev-factory

# ── the bound family kit (recommended) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Without a kit, spec-author's REVIEW gate (spec-quality) has nothing to run. Point at a kit plugin.
# DEV_FACTORY_KIT=/path/to/nonoun-plugins/dev-factory/dev-kit-corpus

# ── the kernel bin (defaults to ../dev-kernel/bin, relative to the dev-server) ────────────────────────────
# DEV_KERNEL_BIN=/path/to/nonoun-plugins/dev-factory/dev-kernel/bin

# ── transport ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HOST=127.0.0.1
# PORT=8731

# ── the bounded autonomous loop (Walk) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Walk (1) = the 30s heartbeat dispatches ready work; Crawl (0) = human-driven, nothing auto-runs.
# run.sh DEFAULTS this to Walk (1) — launching the server IS a user-initiated run; set 0 below to opt into Crawl.
# This does NOT spend tokens on its own: token cost comes from the ADAPTER (set DEV_FACTORY_ADAPTER=headless for
# real `claude` workers). Heartbeat ON + the default mock adapter is the free deterministic loop, bounded by the cap.
# DEV_FACTORY_HEARTBEAT=0           # uncomment to run human-driven (Crawl) instead of the default Walk

# Bound the loop when the heartbeat is ON (run.sh defaults MAX_DISPATCHES=6 if you forget — never unbounded):
# DEV_FACTORY_MAX_DISPATCHES=6      # hard cap on dispatches this window
# DEV_FACTORY_DEADLINE_S=1800       # wall-clock budget (seconds)
# DEV_FACTORY_TOKEN_CEILING=2000000 # token budget
# DEV_FACTORY_TIER=2                # autonomy tier the loop runs at (>=1)
# DEV_FACTORY_CONCURRENCY=2         # parallel workers per tick
# DEV_FACTORY_PERIOD=30             # seconds between ticks
